### ============================================
### AUTH
### ============================================

### Registrar admin (solo en development)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@ceplatam.com",
  "password": "Admin2024!"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@ceplatam.com",
  "password": "Admin2024!"
}

### ============================================
### ISSUERS (POST requiere Authorization: Bearer <token>)
### ============================================

### Crear issuer
POST http://localhost:3000/api/issuers
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Centro de Excelencia Profesional",
  "url": "https://ceplatam.com",
  "email": "badges@ceplatam.com",
  "description": "Emisor oficial de credenciales digitales"
}

### Obtener todos los issuers
GET http://localhost:3000/api/issuers

### Crear badge class
POST http://localhost:3000/api/badge-classes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "issuer_id": "C4AA687A-E954-42F6-BBF1-129E1FD2ABD7",
  "name": "Desarrollo Web Full Stack",
  "description": "Credencial para profesionales en desarrollo web moderno",
  "criteria_narrative": "Completar 120 horas de formación y aprobar evaluación final",
  "achievement_type": "Certificate"
}

### Listar badge classes
GET http://localhost:3000/api/badge-classes


### Crear recipient
POST http://localhost:3000/api/recipients
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Juan Pérez",
  "email": "juan.perez@email.com"
}

### Listar recipients
GET http://localhost:3000/api/recipients



### Emitir badge
POST http://localhost:3000/api/assertions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "badge_class_id": "41F6CB38-9B5B-4766-87C5-2F34F3424C1F",
  "recipient_id": "193DBD3F-6DDF-4A5F-B548-073472C66785"
}


### Emitir badge con firma
POST http://localhost:3000/api/assertions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "badge_class_id": "41F6CB38-9B5B-4766-87C5-2F34F3424C1F",
  "recipient_id": "193DBD3F-6DDF-4A5F-B548-073472C66785"
}

### Crear segundo recipient
POST http://localhost:3000/api/recipients
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "María García",
  "email": "maria.garcia@email.com"
}

### Emitir badge con firma - María García
POST http://localhost:3000/api/assertions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "badge_class_id": "41F6CB38-9B5B-4766-87C5-2F34F3424C1F",
  "recipient_id": "FFD303C3-3DBA-4E8F-8E3F-8F0E0EABCF97"
}

### Crear tercer recipient
POST http://localhost:3000/api/recipients
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Carlos López",
  "email": "carlos.lopez@email.com"
}

### Emitir badge con firma - Carlos López
POST http://localhost:3000/api/assertions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "badge_class_id": "41F6CB38-9B5B-4766-87C5-2F34F3424C1F",
  "recipient_id": "FAA63E40-1DAB-4CE0-91AF-9D08D694C0C6"
}



### Verificar badge de Carlos López
GET http://localhost:3000/verify/9062C82C-6C52-442D-8323-11A930444D4E

### Solo estado
GET http://localhost:3000/verify/9062C82C-6C52-442D-8323-11A930444D4E/status

### ============================================
### REVOCACIÓN
### ============================================

### Revocar assertion de Carlos López
POST http://localhost:3000/api/assertions/9062C82C-6C52-442D-8323-11A930444D4E/revoke
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Certificado emitido por error - datos incorrectos del recipient"
}

### Verificar badge revocado (debe retornar valid: false)
GET http://localhost:3000/verify/9062C82C-6C52-442D-8323-11A930444D4E/status

### ============================================
### STATUS LIST (lista pública de revocaciones)
### ============================================

### Obtener lista de credenciales revocadas
GET http://localhost:3000/api/status-list

### ============================================
### DID & ISSUER PROFILE
### ============================================

### DID Document (did:web resolution)
GET http://localhost:3000/.well-known/did.json

### Perfil público del issuer (Open Badges 3.0 Profile)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/issuers/C4AA687A-E954-42F6-BBF1-129E1FD2ABD7/profile